title: Surakarta
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small, cozy, and popular Indonesian restaurant in the center of Leiden, very close to the two main shopping streets. Serves one vegetarian starter (spring roll filled with vegetables) and five set vegetarian meals. It is also possible to make a choice of the various separate vegetarian dishes available (vegetables, eggs, bean curd). Specializes in dishes from Mid-Java which are only moderately spicy, but more spicy dishes are also available. Non-smoking policy, as obligatory in The Netherlands for all restaurants.
